So, this last center,

13
00:02:15,743 --> 00:02:26,320
 the Sahastrara, is contained in the limbic area of the brain.

14
00:02:32,761 --> 00:02:38,686
Our head is like a coconut.

15
00:02:38,886 --> 00:02:45,749
The coconut has the hair, and then a hard nut

16
00:02:45,949 --> 00:02:49,833
and then a black covering

17
00:02:50,033 --> 00:02:59,636
and inside is white shell

18
00:02:59,837 --> 00:03:04,946
of coconut and inside is the space, the water.

19
00:03:06,401 --> 00:03:10,772
In the same way, our brain is made.

20
00:03:10,972 --> 00:03:15,241
That's why coconut is called as Shreephala.

21
00:03:15,441 --> 00:03:26,555
Is the fruit of the power that is Shree.

22
00:03:26,755 --> 00:03:33,258
Shree power is the right side power

23
00:03:33,458 --> 00:03:38,125
and the left side power is the Lalita power.

24
00:03:38,325 --> 00:03:43,883
So, we have two Chakras - left side, here, is the Lalita

25
00:03:44,083 --> 00:03:50,781
and right side, here, is the Shree Chakra.

26
00:03:50,981 --> 00:03:57,422
These two Chakras are working out

27
00:03:57,622 --> 00:04:00,883
the right side Mahasaraswati's power

28
00:04:01,083 --> 00:04:06,223
and left side Mahakali's powers.

29
00:04:08,719 --> 00:04:14,938
Now, the central power is the Kundalini.

30
00:04:15,138 --> 00:04:21,907
That has to rise and penetrate through different Chakras,

31
00:04:22,107 --> 00:04:30,227
enter into the limbic area and enlighten the seven Pithas -

32
00:04:30,427 --> 00:04:34,290
seats of these seven Chakras.

33
00:04:34,490 --> 00:04:37,853
So, it penetrates through six Chakras,

34
00:04:38,053 --> 00:04:44,228
enters into the limbic area,

35
00:04:44,428 --> 00:04:52,834
enlightens all the seven Pithas in the brain,

36
00:04:53,034 --> 00:04:59,279
which are placed along the mid-line of the limbic area.

37
00:04:59,479 --> 00:05:03,607
So, we start it from the back, is placed here,

38
00:05:03,807 --> 00:05:08,255
at the back, is the Mooladhara Chakra.

39
00:05:08,455 --> 00:05:14,903
Around it is the Swadishthana,

40
00:05:15,103 --> 00:05:20,255
then is the Nabhi, then the Heart,

41
00:05:20,455 --> 00:05:25,013
then the Vishuddhi and then the Agnya.

42
00:05:25,213 --> 00:05:31,536
So, all these six centers are combining

43
00:05:31,736 --> 00:05:35,302
to make the seventh center.

44
00:05:35,502 --> 00:05:39,732
This is a very important point, which we should know.

45
00:05:39,932 --> 00:05:43,504
Now, the Shree Chakra is the right side working

46
00:05:43,705 --> 00:05:47,793
and the Lalita Chakra is the left side working.

47
00:05:47,994 --> 00:05:54,231
So, when the Kundalini doesn't rise

48
00:05:54,432 --> 00:05:59,786
then we do with our right side

49
00:05:59,987 --> 00:06:03,536
our physical and mental activities.

50
00:06:03,737 --> 00:06:07,270
So our brain is doing right side activity

51
00:06:07,471 --> 00:06:12,838
and that's why our brain is like Shreephala.

52
00:06:17,486 --> 00:06:22,090
Sahastrara is actually

53
00:06:22,291 --> 00:06:28,567
is the assemblage of these six Chakras

54
00:06:28,768 --> 00:06:31,301
and is a hollow space,

55
00:06:31,502 --> 00:06:36,098
on the sides of it there are one thousand Nadis.

56
00:06:36,299 --> 00:06:42,692
And when the light penetrates into the limbic area,

57
00:06:42,893 --> 00:06:50,871
then the enlightenment of these Nadis take place

58
00:06:51,072 --> 00:06:54,519
and you can see them as flames,

59
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:58,605
very gentle flames burning

60
00:06:58,806 --> 00:07:02,418
and these flames have all the seven colors

61
00:07:02,619 --> 00:07:08,142
that you see in the vibjyor.

62
00:07:09,611 --> 00:07:14,980
But the last one, ultimately becomes again integrated

63
00:07:15,181 --> 00:07:18,168
and it is a crystal clear flame.

64
00:07:18,369 --> 00:07:25,400
All these seven lights ultimately become crystal clear.

65
00:07:26,154 --> 00:07:31,230
So, you have Sahastrara with one thousand petals,

66
00:07:31,431 --> 00:07:34,152
as they called it,

67
00:07:34,353 --> 00:07:40,191
but if you cut the brain in a transverse section

68
00:07:40,392 --> 00:07:44,761
or horizontal section, you will be able to see

69
00:07:44,962 --> 00:07:50,097
that all these nerves are built like this

70
00:07:50,298 --> 00:07:54,824
along the limbic area, all of them are like a petal,

71
00:07:55,025 --> 00:08:00,566
and if you cut it like this, you will find that

72
00:08:00,767 --> 00:08:08,329
there are many nerves in every bundle of nerves.

73
00:08:09,635 --> 00:08:12,022
So, when it is enlightened,

74
00:08:12,223 --> 00:08:26,058
you can see Sahastrara as a burning bundle of flames.

75
00:08:31,618 --> 00:08:37,438
When I'm speaking you should not do all these things, please.

76
00:08:41,424 --> 00:08:45,908
They are still coming and just disturbing Me.

77
00:08:47,393 --> 00:08:52,127
This a very deep subject.

78
00:08:56,918 --> 00:09:01,725
So the, when the enlightenment of the Kundalini

79
00:09:01,926 --> 00:09:08,139
takes place in the brain,

80
00:09:08,340 --> 00:09:15,373
then the truth is perceived through your brain.

81
00:09:15,574 --> 00:09:18,007
That's why it's called as Satyakhand, means

82
00:09:18,208 --> 00:09:25,046
you start seeing the truth perceived by your brain

83
00:09:25,247 --> 00:09:29,562
because so far whatever you see through your brain,

84
00:09:29,763 --> 00:09:33,359
is not the truth.

85
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:37,132
What you see, is just the outer side,

86
00:09:37,333 --> 00:09:40,046
say, you can see the colors.

87
00:09:40,247 --> 00:09:44,655
You can see the different aesthetics of the colors.

88
00:09:44,856 --> 00:09:48,850
You can see the quality of the thing.

89
00:09:49,051 --> 00:09:53,569
But you cannot say

90
00:09:53,770 --> 00:09:59,592
whether this carpet has been used by some saint.

91
00:09:59,793 --> 00:10:03,391
You cannot say whether this is made by a devil

92
00:10:03,592 --> 00:10:07,313
or a divine person.

93
00:10:07,514 --> 00:10:10,774
You cannot say that this gentleman,

94
00:10:10,975 --> 00:10:17,290
is he a good person or he is an evil person.

95
00:10:17,491 --> 00:10:21,142
You cannot say if this Deity

96
00:10:21,343 --> 00:10:26,205
has come out of the Mother Earth or not.

97
00:10:26,406 --> 00:10:36,302
Also, you cannot say about any person,

98
00:10:36,503 --> 00:10:38,694
who is your relation,

99
00:10:38,895 --> 00:10:48,319
whether he is a good relation or a bad relation,

100
00:10:48,520 --> 00:10:50,598
or what sort of a person he is,

101
00:10:50,799 --> 00:10:54,700
whether he goes to wrong people or to the right people,

102
00:10:54,901 --> 00:10:58,106
whether he has connections with wrong side

103
00:10:58,307 --> 00:11:00,892
or with good side.

104
00:11:01,093 --> 00:11:05,384
Here good means Divine. So actually you do not know

105
00:11:05,585 --> 00:11:10,204
anything about divinity with your mind, nothing.

106
00:11:10,405 --> 00:11:14,290
Nothing - is impossible for you to judge a person

107
00:11:14,491 --> 00:11:17,543
about his divinity unless and until the Kundalini

108
00:11:17,744 --> 00:11:22,402
reaches at least this part, which is the limbic area.

109
00:11:22,603 --> 00:11:27,238
You cannot make out whether a person is real or not,

110
00:11:27,439 --> 00:11:31,488
whether a guru is real or not.

111
00:11:31,689 --> 00:11:38,301
Because divinity cannot be perceived through your brain,

112
00:11:38,502 --> 00:11:46,275
unless and until this light of your Spirit shines into it.

113
00:11:47,466 --> 00:11:50,523
Now, the Spirit is expressed in the heart,

114
00:11:50,724 --> 00:11:52,724
is reflected in the heart,

115
00:11:52,925 --> 00:11:56,919
the center of the Spirit, we can say, is in the heart.

116
00:11:57,120 --> 00:12:02,388
But actually, the seat of Spirit is above, here

117
00:12:02,589 --> 00:12:07,044
And that is the Spirit what we call of the God Almighty,

118
00:12:07,245 --> 00:12:16,383
Who say, Whom you call [SOUNDS LIKE Parvardigar],

119
00:12:16,584 --> 00:12:20,016
you call Him Sadashiva

120
00:12:20,217 --> 00:12:27,899
or you can call Him, ah, the Rahim

121
00:12:28,100 --> 00:12:30,633
and you can call Him by many names

122
00:12:30,834 --> 00:12:36,117
which are said about

123
00:12:36,318 --> 00:12:41,305
the Lord who is God Almighty.

124
00:12:41,506 --> 00:12:45,289
Neeranjan, they call It, Neerankar,

125
00:12:45,490 --> 00:12:50,930
every sort of words which start with Nira, Nihi.

126
00:12:51,131 --> 00:12:57,502
Now, at every center

127
00:12:57,703 --> 00:13:02,693
in the body you'll receive a different type of joy.

128
00:13:03,969 --> 00:13:07,210
Every center has a different type of joy

129
00:13:07,411 --> 00:13:10,327
and there are names for every types of joy

130
00:13:10,528 --> 00:13:14,788
you receive at every center when the Kundalini rises.

131
00:13:14,989 --> 00:13:19,343
But when the Kundalini comes into the Sahastrara,

132
00:13:19,544 --> 00:13:24,320
then the joy you receive is called as Neerananda,

133
00:13:24,521 --> 00:13:26,067
Neerananda.

134
00:13:26,268 --> 00:13:33,674
Now, Nee means nothing else but Ananda. Neerananda.

135
00:13:35,527 --> 00:13:38,646
Also, is surprising, My name is Neera -

136
00:13:38,847 --> 00:13:42,310
also, in My family I'm called as Neera.

137
00:13:42,511 --> 00:13:46,583
And Neera also means Mary, Maria.

138
00:13:46,784 --> 00:13:49,849
Because it means marine. Neera is water.

139
00:13:50,050 --> 00:13:52,841
Neera means water in Sanskrit language.

140
00:13:53,042 --> 00:13:57,646
It is called as Neerananda in the brain.

141
00:13:57,847 --> 00:14:02,427
And this stage ultimately unfolds.

142
00:14:02,628 --> 00:14:07,607
First what you know is the Satya, is the Truth -

143
00:14:07,808 --> 00:14:13,107
what is this another gentleman is suffering from,

144
00:14:13,308 --> 00:14:17,646
that you see on your fingers. First you see your fingers.

145
00:14:17,847 --> 00:14:21,459
With your attention you know what Chakras,

146
00:14:21,660 --> 00:14:24,482
what fingers are catching, with your attention.

147
00:14:24,683 --> 00:14:28,576
Then with your brain you can depict

148
00:14:28,777 --> 00:14:31,068
what center, which is catching.

149
00:14:31,269 --> 00:14:33,269
Because, if you say this finger,

150
00:14:33,470 --> 00:14:36,324
that doesn't mean it is Vishuddhi Chakra.

151
00:14:36,525 --> 00:14:40,519
But your brain then says, "It is Vishuddhi."

152
00:14:40,720 --> 00:14:44,688
And that depicts it that this fellow is suffering

153
00:14:44,889 --> 00:14:48,297
from the troubles of the Vishuddhi Chakra.

154
00:14:48,498 --> 00:14:51,578
But still it is rational.

155
00:14:51,779 --> 00:14:56,109
Because you see what finger it catches and then you say it.

156
00:14:56,310 --> 00:15:04,581
But when the Satyakhanda or the Sahastrara unfolds itself more,

157
00:15:04,782 --> 00:15:10,305
you don't have to think about it, you just say it.

158
00:15:12,126 --> 00:15:18,675
Then there is no difference between your Chitta and your Satya.

159
00:15:18,876 --> 00:15:28,328
The enlightened Chitta and the enlightened brain become one.

160
00:15:29,930 --> 00:15:32,737
There is no problem at all for such a person,

161
00:15:32,938 --> 00:15:36,244
there's no need to see on the fingers, no need to say

162
00:15:36,445 --> 00:15:40,291
anything on the fingers and then depict it through brain.

163
00:15:40,492 --> 00:15:42,955
Which you have learnt in Sahaja Yoga,

164
00:15:43,156 --> 00:15:47,432
that if you find something wrong here, it means Agnya -

165
00:15:47,633 --> 00:15:52,265
that's not necessary! You just say Agnya.

166
00:15:53,867 --> 00:15:57,859
And you just say it and it is there.

167
00:15:58,390 --> 00:16:04,173
Then it unfolds more.

168
00:16:04,374 --> 00:16:09,306
First it is integrated with, as I said, Chitta.

169
00:16:09,507 --> 00:16:18,235
Then, when it gets absolutely integrated with the Spirit,

170
00:16:18,443 --> 00:16:25,607
then whatever you say, is the truth.

171
00:16:27,137 --> 00:16:30,691
You just say it, it is so.

172
00:16:33,668 --> 00:16:42,511
That is how this brain unfolds into three new dimensions.

173
00:16:42,712 --> 00:16:50,754
First, it depicts the truth through logical conclusions.

174
00:16:50,955 --> 00:16:55,059
Because, I have told you that

175
00:16:55,260 --> 00:16:58,739
if this finger is catching then it is Vishuddhi.

176
00:16:58,940 --> 00:17:01,794
And then you ask the person, "Have you got a problem here?"

177
00:17:01,995 --> 00:17:05,278
He says, "Yes". Then you believe in Me

178
00:17:05,479 --> 00:17:08,669
and then you believe that this is the Vishuddhi Chakra,

179
00:17:08,870 --> 00:17:10,870
which is showing, is true.

180
00:17:11,071 --> 00:17:13,739
This is the logical conclusion, in a way,

181
00:17:13,940 --> 00:17:18,012
that you have experimented, you are seeing

182
00:17:18,213 --> 00:17:21,442
and still doubting whether Mother says it's true or not.

183
00:17:21,643 --> 00:17:24,419
And then, you are sure, "Yes, it is so,

184
00:17:24,620 --> 00:17:26,864
we have seen that this is Vishuddhi Chakra." So,

185
00:17:27,065 --> 00:17:30,372
the truth becomes logically acceptable to his brain.

186
00:17:30,573 --> 00:17:35,403
But still, there is the brain working out on its gross level.

187
00:17:35,604 --> 00:17:43,465
Then the second stage, as I told you, where you believe,

188
00:17:43,666 --> 00:17:46,294
you know for definite that this means Vishuddhi Chakra,

189
00:17:46,495 --> 00:17:48,495
no doubt about it. Nobody.

190
00:17:48,696 --> 00:17:51,112
Then - then we start Nirvikalpa has started,

191
00:17:51,313 --> 00:17:54,706
when there's no doubt about Me or Sahaja Yoga.

192
00:17:54,907 --> 00:17:59,417
But then, the new unfolding starts within.

193
00:17:59,618 --> 00:18:04,425
For that, one has to do meditation.

194
00:18:04,626 --> 00:18:10,001
In humility, one has to do meditation.

195
00:18:10,860 --> 00:18:14,261
And then also, for this new dimension,

196
00:18:14,462 --> 00:18:19,353
where your Chitta itself becomes merged

197
00:18:19,554 --> 00:18:24,876
into your brain or into the enlightened brain,

198
00:18:25,077 --> 00:18:30,597
for that one has to very honestly and humbly

199
00:18:30,798 --> 00:18:34,902
surrender to Sahaja Yoga.

200
00:18:35,103 --> 00:18:40,722
Now, what do we do when we get our vibrations?

201
00:18:40,923 --> 00:18:43,199
We have different-different reactions.

202
00:18:43,400 --> 00:18:48,426
Some people do not even understand the value of vibrations.

203
00:18:48,627 --> 00:18:53,837
Some people try to learn what it means.

204
00:18:54,182 --> 00:18:58,269
And some people suddenly think, "O, now they are realized souls,

205
00:18:58,470 --> 00:19:00,925
they can go on giving realizations, this, that."

206
00:19:01,126 --> 00:19:05,774
They go on a ride of a ego-trip.

207
00:19:06,149 --> 00:19:10,503
When they go on a ride of a ego-trip, then they find that

208
00:19:10,704 --> 00:19:12,823
they've failed and they've to come back,

209
00:19:13,024 --> 00:19:16,886
from the very beginning they start. It's like

210
00:19:17,087 --> 00:19:21,438
the game of Snake & Ladder.

211
00:19:22,150 --> 00:19:27,932
So, reaction to vibration should be

212
00:19:28,133 --> 00:19:33,455
a very humble, receptive reaction.

213
00:19:33,656 --> 00:19:39,494
Now, on the gross level, because as I told you that the brain

214
00:19:39,695 --> 00:19:46,002
is the one which holds the Father in it.

215
00:19:46,203 --> 00:19:51,229
So, if we commit any sins against the Father,

216
00:19:51,446 --> 00:19:58,140
then this unfoldment in the brain takes some time.

217
00:19:59,135 --> 00:20:03,247
So, we start reading books.

218
00:20:03,448 --> 00:20:06,230
And though people have told that first see the vibrations

219
00:20:06,431 --> 00:20:08,431
and then read the books, still we say, "O, what's wrong,

220
00:20:08,632 --> 00:20:11,363
we should read other books."

221
00:20:11,564 --> 00:20:15,121
You go down again, Snake and Ladder, as I said.

222
00:20:15,322 --> 00:20:19,861
That is one of the snakes.

223
00:20:20,744 --> 00:20:22,744
We think that, "What's the need to do meditation,

224
00:20:22,945 --> 00:20:28,142
I've no time, I have this thing, that thing." You do not progress.

225
00:20:30,528 --> 00:20:32,921
The other point which is very gross.

226
00:20:33,122 --> 00:20:36,288
Also, there are some very gross people in Sahaja Yoga

227
00:20:36,489 --> 00:20:39,476
who enter into it. Doesn't matter.

228
00:20:39,677 --> 00:20:42,322
But first thing you must know you have to be honest,

229
00:20:42,523 --> 00:20:45,947
very honest in Sahaja Yoga.

230
00:20:46,148 --> 00:20:50,275
The honesty is like - I have seen people.

231
00:20:50,476 --> 00:20:54,713
If we have a dinner, say, for a marriage-party,

232
00:20:54,914 --> 00:20:58,572
they'll just crawl into it without having any self-respect,

233
00:20:58,773 --> 00:21:01,076
without having any understanding as to

234
00:21:01,277 --> 00:21:04,373
who is going to pay for the all this? They'll bring all their family,

235
00:21:04,574 --> 00:21:07,545
come down and sit down.

236
00:21:07,746 --> 00:21:13,092
There are people who avoid paying money

237
00:21:13,293 --> 00:21:17,295
which should be paid for Sahaja Yoga.

238
00:21:17,496 --> 00:21:20,303
Supposing, they're eating food or they are travelling

239
00:21:20,504 --> 00:21:24,389
or they're coming from abroad,

240
00:21:24,590 --> 00:21:28,623
they have to pay money for their travelling, for their food.

241
00:21:28,824 --> 00:21:32,318
And, sometimes, you know I have to pay lot of money.

242
00:21:32,519 --> 00:21:35,770
Doesn't matter, I don't mind. But is not good for you,

243
00:21:35,971 --> 00:21:39,340
the main thing it's not good for you.

244
00:21:39,541 --> 00:21:42,961
So, how you behave towards Sahaja Yoga

245
00:21:43,162 --> 00:21:45,930
as far as money is concerned is also very important,

246
00:21:46,131 --> 00:21:50,211
though it looks gross. But it can give a big trouble

247
00:21:50,412 --> 00:21:54,922
in the unfoldment because of the Nabhi catching

248
00:21:55,123 --> 00:21:58,070
and, as you know, if the Nabhi catches

249
00:21:58,271 --> 00:22:02,195
it can spread up to the whole of void.

250
00:22:02,396 --> 00:22:05,656
And if the void is catching Ekadesha Rudra,

251
00:22:05,857 --> 00:22:10,880
