01:17:06,427 --> 01:17:13,200
first thing. Secondly, how does he live, what is his style of life.

978
01:17:13,849 --> 01:17:19,593
Thirdly what others have achieved, what is their condition.

979
01:17:19,794 --> 01:17:23,687
Most of the disciples of transcendental meditations

980
01:17:23,888 --> 01:17:27,015
are now beggars on the street.

981
01:17:27,216 --> 01:17:29,687
And some of them are epileptic patients,

982
01:17:29,888 --> 01:17:34,794
I have seen so many getting epilepsy.

983
01:17:35,764 --> 01:17:39,899
So if you have done transcendental meditation it is not meditation

984
01:17:40,100 --> 01:17:42,454
but it is anti-God thing.

985
01:17:42,655 --> 01:17:44,884
So you have to first neutralize yourself,

986
01:17:45,085 --> 01:17:47,085
come down to normal conditions

987
01:17:47,286 --> 01:17:49,585
and then you receive your Realization.

988
01:17:49,786 --> 01:17:52,757
We have a lady here who was a granddaughter of a Duke.

989
01:17:52,958 --> 01:17:55,976
She lost all her money and her husband was the director

990
01:17:56,177 --> 01:17:59,656
of one of these "flying squads" that he was having.

991
01:17:59,857 --> 01:18:01,857
He lost all his money and became bankrupt,

992
01:18:02,058 --> 01:18:06,248
this lady got epilepsy, he got epilepsy, her child got epilepsy,

993
01:18:06,449 --> 01:18:09,350
all of them got epilepsy. They came to Sahaja Yoga

994
01:18:09,551 --> 01:18:13,389
when they had nothing with them. Today they are all right,

995
01:18:13,590 --> 01:18:17,420
all corrected and they are doing well.

996
01:18:17,621 --> 01:18:21,147
But we do not take a guarantee on anything

997
01:18:21,348 --> 01:18:24,544
because you have to also decide in your mind

998
01:18:24,745 --> 01:18:26,745
that you are not going to have this funny ideas

999
01:18:26,946 --> 01:18:29,878
because some of the TM people who come are so arrogant

1000
01:18:30,079 --> 01:18:33,503
so egoistical, that it is impossible to manage them.

1001
01:18:33,704 --> 01:18:36,526
So it is your need, not our need

1002
01:18:36,727 --> 01:18:40,159
and that's how you should come to a doctor as a patient comes.

1003
01:18:40,360 --> 01:18:46,227
Then only it will work out. Otherwise don't waste our time, please.

1004
01:18:50,834 --> 01:18:54,826
That? Now all the questions are over

1005
01:18:55,027 --> 01:19:01,159
and for the last time let us go into meditation here in this hall.

1006
01:19:05,273 --> 01:19:10,929
[Hindi]

